OL,4,CGovernment urged to create post-Covid
OL,5,C'golden age' of cycling
OL,6, The government can create a "golden age
OL,7, of cycling" if it capitalises on the
OL,8, surge of interest in it during
OL,9, lockdown, a transport charity has said.
OL,11,FAt one point last year, almost four
OL,12,Ftimes as many journeys as usual were
OL,13,Fbeing taken by bike, but usage has gone
OL,14,Fback to normal levels since then.
OL,16,FThe charity Sustrans says cyclists need
OL,17,Fto feel safer and wants more 20mph
OL,18,Fzones and more effective cycle lanes.
OL,20,FThe government said it had "ambitious
OL,21,Fplans to boost walking and cycling".
